    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，P3-T2_complete是已经完成的任务，用done标记。另外P1有两个执行阶段：T1_exec和T1_exec2，中间有间隔。P3的T1_exec要在P2的T1_exec之后开始。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1-T1_exec",
        "P1-T1_exec2",
        "P3-T1_exec",
        "P2-T1_exec"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建基础框架，设置时间格式为X轴毫秒显示。P1-T1_exec放在16-20毫秒，P1-T1_exec2放在26-30毫秒。P2-T1_exec接在P1-T1_exec后面，20-24毫秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat X",
        "axisFormat %sms",
        "p1t1b",
        "p1t1c",
        "p2t1b"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要加一个I/O Operations的section，里面放一个里程碑P2-T2_IO_end，在16毫秒那个时间点。这是整个流程的起始触发点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "I/O Operations",
        "P2-T2_IO_end",
        "milestone",
        "io_end"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，16毫秒处加里程碑。那P2-T2_exec放在30-34毫秒，P2-T1_final放在34-38毫秒收尾。P3的T1_exec是24-26毫秒，T2_complete也是24-26毫秒，这两个是并行的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T2_exec",
