    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是的，P3那两个任务时间重叠，但T2_complete是done状态，T1_exec是active状态。另外所有active的任务都用active标签标记。",
      "elements_involved": [
